What are the parameters about this json-rpc request? Is there any documentation on this? I get the err "expected value at line 2 column 24" abput :
curl --location 'https://starknet-goerli.g.alchemy.com/v2/PBvB1f_YUOZpvd-zz1g9PNTzYL48jaSV' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data '{
    "jsonrpc": "2.0", 
    "method": "starknet_getBlockWithTxHashes", 
    "params":
        {
            "block_id":833534
        },
    "id": ""
    }'
How to deal with the err ?

I don't think the node is a Juno node. Also, the request data should be as follows:
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "starknet_getBlockWithTxHashes",
  "params": {
    "block_id": {
      "block_number": 833534
    }
  },
  "id": 0
}
